      "title": "Coal Tender awarded to lowest bidder",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The Minister of Power and Energy says that a tender was awarded yesterday (25) to the lowest bid received for the procurement of Coal for the Norochcholai Plant based on the procurement process followed by evaluation & approval from STEC, SSCAPC.",
        "\"Supplier will provide 6 months credit facility from the date of supply of each shipment\". Minister Wijesekara said.",
